challengeURL.description:
challengeURL is a URL to redirect unauthenticated /authorize requests to Unauthenticated requests from OAuth clients which expect WWW-Authenticate challenges will be redirected here. ${url} is replaced with the current URL, escaped to be safe in a query parameter
  https://www.example.com/sso-login?then=${url}
${query} is replaced with the current query string
  https://www.example.com/auth-proxy/oauth/authorize?${query}
Required when challenge is set to true.

